PN,36502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1778864757
OL,3,CWhy a gorilla statue could cost
OL,4,Chomeowner #20,000 in planning row
OL,6,F"I just like it it's different no one
OL,7,Felse has got one up on the wall have
OL,8,Fthey. I like a bit of quirky. There's
OL,9,Fnowt else I can say.
OL,11,F"He's not harming anyone, he's
OL,12,Fplastic, he's just a plastic
OL,13,Fgorilla... people need to get a life,"
OL,14,Fshe added.
OL,16,FCaesar sat outside her previous home
OL,17,Fin the Belle Isle area of Leeds for 15
OL,18,Fyears where she said she had no
OL,19,Fissues, until she moved to Wakefield.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,366,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1778864757
OL,3,CWhy a gorilla statue could cost
OL,4,Chomeowner #20,000 in planning row
OL,6,FAdele has appealed against a council
OL,7,Fruling that Caesar was breaching
OL,8,Fplanning rules but it was rejected by
OL,9,Fthe independent inspectorate.
OL,11,FShe's been ordered to remove her
OL,12,Fplastic pet by June 9 or face a hefty
OL,13,Ffine.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,366,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1778864757
OL,3,CWhy a gorilla statue could cost
OL,4,Chomeowner #20,000 in planning row
OL,6,F"Look I don't want to go to court I
OL,7,Fdon't want to go to magistrates I
OL,8,Fdon't want to go to crown court
OL,9,Fbecause this is what they're saying
OL,10,Fand it's going to cost around twenty
OL,11,Fthousand pounds which is absolutely
OL,12,Fridiculous over a plastic monkey at
OL,13,Fthe end of the day but I will find a
OL,14,Fbetter spot for it in my garden."
OL,16,FIn a statement, Joe Jenkinson,
OL,17,FWakefield Council's Service Director
OL,18,Ffor Planning, Transportation and
OL,19,FStrategic Highways, said no one is
OL,20,Fasking to "get rid" of Caesar.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,366,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1778864757
OL,3,CWhy a gorilla statue could cost
OL,4,Chomeowner #20,000 in planning row
OL,6,F"The Planning Inspectorate is
OL,7,Fcompletely independent of the Council,
OL,8,Fand having looked at it impartially,
OL,9,Fhave dismissed the owner's appeal and
OL,10,Fupheld the enforcement notice.
OL,12,F"This means the gorilla statue will
OL,13,Fneed to be removed from its current
OL,14,Fsite within four weeks. No-one is
OL,15,Fasking her to get rid of Caesar. It
OL,16,Fjust can't go there."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
